metadata.name: Days Off
metadata.description:
Snoozing in my underground lair, having earned a respite from my customary mission of eliminating the city's most deadly criminals. As I soak in an empty tub, I can't help but think about how I rose to become the most feared mercenary in town. 

Outside my secret sanctuary, the lights of the busy city serve as a reminder of the mayhem I so frequently find myself in, but for the time being, I am pleased to simply revel in the peace.
